{"tid":2403383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我有宗教信仰，唔會用安心上路 aka 777獸印，獸印=用心理學機制將人訓練成畜牲獸類","createTime":"2021-02-11T05:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T05:50:58.000Z","uid":35776,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3d242ec1ee232bad52faf628cb7d8ff55be72216","tid":2403383,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T05:11:45.000Z","msg":"啟 示 錄 13 (16 - 17)<br />\n他 又 叫 眾 人 ， 無 論 大 小 、 貧 富 、 自 主 的 、 為 奴 的 ， 都 在 右 手 上 或 是 在 額 上 受 一 個 印 記 。除 了 那 受 印 記 、 有 了 獸 名 或 有 獸 名 數 目 的 ， 都 不 得 做 買 賣 。<br />\n<br />\n防疫政策就係應用訓練動物既 「<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"purple\">巴夫洛夫效應</span></span></strong>」，用限聚令，599G，禁堂食，口罩令，不斷設置新制約手段，再用放鬆制約作為獎勵機制，對正常生活既普通人訓練成為圈家畜，墮落成獸<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">心理學上，有個很有名的學說，就是「條件反射」\n俄國的心理學家，「巴夫洛夫」曾經做過一個實驗，\n \n將一隻狗，給關了起來，之後，每當在餵食之前，先等一下，等牠先流夠了「口水」之後，再給牠吃！\n \n之後，只要要吃飯了，狗就會在看到食物時，先不自主的流口水！\n \n爾後，進入第二階段。當在給狗食物前，會先有「鈴聲」，之後，同時出現食物讓狗看，\n於是，狗就流口水！\n \n再一而再，再而三的玩個幾次，\n鈴聲+食物！\n讓狗流口水！\n \n結果，狗就被心理學所稱的「制約」現像給制約了！\n \n之後，拿走食物，只要聽到「鈴聲」！狗就會不由自主的「流口水」！\n \n這又叫「制約反射」或是「條件反射」！又稱為是「古典制約」！\n \n這些狗在被「制約」下，學會了，「鈴聲」等於「食物」，有了「食物」就等於要「流口水」！\n \n全都不由自主！\n \n這種現象，看起來很好玩，可是很可憐，動物的學習，大多數是靠這種「不用腦」去思考，而靠著身體的反射現象，來學習事物。</code></pre>"},{"pid":"81b2126bd7ab6711833f6c67bbb5522662592352","tid":2403383,"uid":204401,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T05:14:19.000Z","msg":"最多咪唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8201a3443f64456835d2ce33d5dc095918a01c","tid":2403383,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T05:18:13.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58fe848d13152c623589451fa264a496ff2f16a","tid":2403383,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T05:18:14.000Z","msg":"七七七獸印 網民齊聲贊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i-lih-kg.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2850000%2F2853605%2Fbus_thumb_20210115_ch_1024.jpg&amp;h=9b914344&amp;s=540\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi-lih-kg.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fi.lih.kg%2Fthumbnail%3Fu%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%252Fres%252Fv3%252Fimage%252Fcontent%252F2850000%252F2853605%252Fbus_thumb_20210115_ch_1024.jpg%26h%3D9b914344%26s%3D540&h=0a34c5ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20932b5845b78dcd04cf633ff1323549b8d6075d","tid":2403383,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T05:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e0dc3de706a334776e0e7163f15fdcf7def714","tid":2403383,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T05:28:29.000Z","msg":"安心上路，裝佢老母 ！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1effc1f07bed294d9f4f6298d76a4e46e25002","tid":2403383,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T05:34:24.000Z","msg":"逢人一律答信教唔裝獸印app"},{"pid":"f80254ee586ce44de88f695554795b5faee82166","tid":2403383,"uid":76404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T05:35:45.000Z","msg":"越嚟越似"},{"pid":"f8504ba2e03635f226ef27171da4ab4eaaa4a226","tid":2403383,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3d242ec1ee232bad52faf628cb7d8ff55be72216","tid":2403383,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T05:11:45.000Z","msg"